gHellanzb                                                                 README


                 Gnome applet monitoring hellanzb
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

REQUIREMENTS :
______________

    hellanzb >= 0.13    http://www.hellanzb.com/distfiles
    Unix O/S            E.g.: http://www.ubuntu.org
    Python >= 2.3       http://www.python.org
    pygtk >= 2.4        http://www.pygtk.org
    python-gnome
    python-gnome-extras (or python-gnome-desktop if you're using GNOME >= 2.14)
    
    

INSTALLING :
____________

The latest release is available at:

    http://nicoworkspace.free.fr/?q=ghellanzb-downloads

gHellanzb is available in three formats:
    o deb package for Ubuntu >= 8.04, including dependancies,
    o deb package for Ubuntu >= 8.04, without the dependancies (if you have 
      installed hellanzb from the source package instead of using the deb 
      package),
    o source package if you want to have a look at the codes, or if you want to 
      install it yourself.

CONFIGURING :
_____________

gHellanzb does not need configuration. What you need to do is look at the 
hellanzb.conf file (usually /etc/hellanzb.conf), to check that the 
following variables are enabled and configured:

    Hellanzb.XMLRPC_SERVER = 'localhost'

    Hellanzb.XMLRPC_PORT = 8760

    Hellanzb.XMLRPC_PASSWORD = 'changeme'
    


